wing: visual_learning_sorting
rooms:
- name: todo
  description: Files from TODO/
- name: documentation
  description: Files from docs/
- name: general
  description: Files that don't fit other rooms
- name: decisions
  description: Locked architectural and design decisions, decision records, and choices
    that govern implementation
- name: algorithm-contracts
  description: Algorithm tick sequences, animation contracts, sort step definitions,
    T1 compare T2 swap T3 tree T4 completion specifications for Bubble Selection Insertion
    and Heap Sort
- name: animation-physics
  description: Sprite motion, arc height, sine curve interpolation, coordinate tracking,
    delta time dt, arc swap, lift and drop, panel layout, and frame rendering specifications
- name: acceptance-tests
  description: Acceptance tests, test plans, AT numbered test cases, pass fail criteria,
    visual correctness verification, and algorithm behavior validation
- name: architecture
  description: MVC structure, src visualizer directory layout, controller model view
    responsibilities, SortResult data contracts, module boundaries, and system organization
